casebody.head_matter:
Yolanda BELL, petitioner,
v.
INOVA HEALTH CARE, dba Inova Fairfax Hospital.
No. 17-7880.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 26, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until April 16, 2018, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
